'''蚁垤庙'''（Bhagwan Valmiki Tirath Asthan）是一座印度教寺庙和重要的历史古迹，供奉古印度仙人[[蚁垤|蚁垤]]（Valmiki），位于印度[[旁遮普邦|旁遮普邦]][[阿姆利则|阿姆利则]]市的蚁垤庙路（Bhagwan Valmiki Tirath road）。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://indianexpress.com/article/cities/chandigarh/panorama-and-museum-important-to-us-valmiki-community-4386771/ |title=Panorama and museum important to us: Valmiki community |date=21 November 2016 |work=The Indian Express |access-date=30 July 2018 |language=en-US |archive-date=2020-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116040811/https://indianexpress.com/article/cities/chandigarh/panorama-and-museum-important-to-us-valmiki-community-4386771/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://punjab.gov.in/key-initiative?view=show&pp_id=3890 |title=Bhagwan Valmiki Tirath Sthal - Government of Punjab, India |website=punjab.gov.in |language=en-US |access-date=30 July 2018 |archive-date=2019-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330043957/http://punjab.gov.in/key-initiative?view=show&pp_id=3890 |dead-url=no }}</ref>自2016年12月1日起，有一个 8 英尺高、<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/chandigarh/For-Dalits-Punjab-rolls-out-a-pre-poll-Valmiki-idol-darshan/articleshow/55506260.cms |title=For Dalits, Punjab rolls out a pre-poll Valmiki idol darshan |work=The Times of India |access-date=30 July 2018 |archive-date=2018-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180825214716/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/chandigarh/For-Dalits-Punjab-rolls-out-a-pre-poll-Valmiki-idol-darshan/articleshow/55506260.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref> 800公斤的[[镀金|镀金]]的[[蚁垤|蚁垤]]雕像。<ref>{{cite web |title=Punjab Govt declares holiday on Dec 1 |website=uni india |date=30 July 2018 |url=http://www.uniindia.com/punjab-govt-declares-holiday-on-dec-1/states/news/696698.html |access-date=30 July 2018 |archive-date=2020-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116040811/http://www.uniindia.com/punjab-govt-declares-holiday-on-dec-1/states/news/696698.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/chandigarh/Grand-plans-for-Dalits-in-Punjab/articleshow/56054865.cms |title=Grand plans for Dalits in Punjab |work=The Times of India |access-date=30 July 2018 |archive-date=2018-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180825214719/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/chandigarh/Grand-plans-for-Dalits-in-Punjab/articleshow/56054865.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref>

寺庙供奉[[蚁垤|蚁垤]]位于阿姆利则以西11公里。寺庙可以追溯到罗摩衍那时期，这里是蚁垤的的修行处。当罗摩的妻子悉多被流放后，圣人在这里庇护她。这里是[[罗摩|罗摩]]与悉多的两个儿子，罗婆与俱舍，都是在这里，[[蚁垤|蚁垤]]的修行处出生。<ref>Hinduism, Dr. S.S. Kapoor, Hemkunt Press, 2005</ref> 据说伟大的史诗《[[罗摩衍那|罗摩衍那]]》是[[蚁垤|蚁垤]]在这里写的。

==开发==
2016年10月18日，蚁垤庙工程奠基，由古鲁·纳纳克大学建筑系设计。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.tribuneindia.com/2013/20131019/punjab.htm#3 |title=CM lays stone for Valmiki Temple at Amritsar |website=www.tribuneindia.com |access-date=30 July 2018 |archive-date=2017-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170225215425/http://www.tribuneindia.com/2013/20131019/punjab.htm#3 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2016年12月1日，旁遮普邦首席部长宣布开放。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://indianexpress.com/article/india/badals-inaugurate-valmiki-temple-in-amritsar-4406041/ |title=Badals inaugurate Valmiki temple in Amritsar |date=2 December 2016 |work=The Indian Express |access-date=30 July 2018 |language=en-US |archive-date=2019-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330032552/https://indianexpress.com/article/india/badals-inaugurate-valmiki-temple-in-amritsar-4406041/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/amritsar/Eyes-on-SC-votes-CM-opens-Valmiki-temple/articleshow/55739471.cms |title=Eyes on SC votes, CM opens Valmiki temple |work=The Times of India |access-date=30 July 2018 |archive-date=2018-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180829170648/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/amritsar/Eyes-on-SC-votes-CM-opens-Valmiki-temple/articleshow/55739471.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref> 
历史遗址经过翻修，设有两端入口、池塘、桥梁、可容纳 5000 人的大殿、梵文图书馆、博物馆和可容纳 500 辆汽车的多层现代停车场。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/punjab/rs-200-crore-renovation-project-over-ram-tirath-shrine-to-open-on-december-1st/story-2n3QWCLdbugaeBa0n8JKXN.html |title=Rs 200-crore renovation project over, Bhagwan Valmiki Tirath shrine to open on December 1st |date=27 November 2016 |work=hindustan times |access-date=30 July 2018 |language=en |archive-date=2019-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330032506/https://www.hindustantimes.com/punjab/rs-200-crore-renovation-project-over-ram-tirath-shrine-to-open-on-december-1st/story-2n3QWCLdbugaeBa0n8JKXN.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://worldarchitecture.org/architecture-projects/gcnn/valmiki_temple_amritsar_punjab-project-pages.html |title=VALMIKI TEMPLE, AMRITSAR, PUNJAB |website=worldarchitecture.org |language=en |access-date=30 July 2018 |archive-date=2019-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330032514/https://worldarchitecture.org/architecture-projects/gcnn/valmiki_temple_amritsar_punjab-project-pages.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

